:;(Obtain a Enhanced  2-star Blessing of Preservation)
:{{DIcon|Star}} Qlipoth's Favor. &mdash; Enhance 2 random Blessings.
:;(Enhance 2 random 1-3 star Blessings)
:{{DIcon|Star}} Qlipoth's Blessing. &mdash; Obtain a 2-star Blessing of Preservation.
:;(Obtain a 2-star Blessing of Preservation)
